N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 212.9 - Venue

State Regulations

Motions for a change of venue shall be heard
in the division of the court in which the action was instituted. An order of
transfer shall direct the disposition of the papers then on
file. Notes
